vote.title: Authorize an addition to Kaufman County Municipal Utility District No. 3 within the City of Dallas’ extraterritorial jurisdiction that would include approximately 14.997 acres on property located in Kaufman County, southeast of University Drive and FM 548 - Financing:  No cost consideration to the City
